quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,16,"Soni chisimu Uwwe tun’gumbile mundu, ni tukumanyilila yaikunsongonela ntima wakwe, soni Uwwe tuli dusi nnope kwa jwalakwe (ni umanyilisi Wetu) kupunda ntasi ŵakuuta myasi (wannukosi mwakwe)."
  50,17,"(Kumbuchilani) katema kaakupochela (itendo ya mundu ni kuilemba) akupochela ŵaŵili (Achimalaika) ŵaakutama chakun’dyo ni chakunchiji."
  50,18,"Ngaakulumukulaga (mundu) liloŵe lililyose, ikaŵeje kukwakwe kukuŵa kwana nkwembecheya jwatayali (kulemba)."
  51,10,"Pamasile palaniwe ŵaunami."
  51,11,"Aŵala ŵaatiŵiile mu ujinga, achikwanjilaga (ya Akhera)."
  51,12,"Akuwusyaga (mwachipongwe): “Ni chakachi (kwika kwakwe lyele) Lisiku Lyamalipilo?”"
  52,1,"Ngulilumbila litumbi (lyaŵam’bechetakasyisye Allah Musa lyalili ku Sinayi)."
  52,2,"Ni chitabu chachilembeedwe (Qur’an)."
  52,3,"Mu ikalakala yepende yewunukulidwe."